OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBelgian royals in DR Congo:
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FKing Philippe laments      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fracism of colonial past    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Belgium's King Philippe has decried the
OL,6, racism meted out in the Democratic     
OL,7, Republic of Congo under the colonial   
OL,8, rule of his ancestors.                 
OL,10,F"This regime was one of unequal        
OL,11,Frelations, unjustifiable in itself,    
OL,12,Fmarked by paternalism, discrimination  
OL,13,Fand racism," he said.                  
OL,15,FKing Philippe is on a week-long visit  
OL,16,Fto DR Congo at the invitation of       
OL,17,FPresident Felix Tshisekedi.            
OL,19,FThe king was speaking in the grounds of
OL,20,FDR Congo's parliament in Kinshasa.     
